      "text": "Question: We have 2 candles, that both burn for 1\nhour. They're both non-linear, means the length of\nthe candle does not show how much longer it will\nburn for. How do we find out if 45 minutes have\npassed?",
      "fontSize": 62.31470946800795,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Question: We have 2 candles, that both burn for 1 hour. They're both non-linear, means the length of the candle does not show how much longer it will burn for. How do we find out if 45 minutes have passed?",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
